en.description: IFAKv2 is a personal medical kit issued to soldiers in service. The official first aid kit in the U.S. Marine Corps IFAK (Individual First Aid Kit of the United States Marine Corps). The Mk2 simply revolves around treating bleeds and traumas removing any unnesscary components.
